--- caveats (raw#10 C3) ---
  1. CLI surface limited: 6 subcmds expose ~core ~10% of qmirror functionality
     (chsh/qrng/iit/phi advanced flags reachable only via direct hexa run).
  2. Real-QPU subcommands (chsh --vendor=ionq|rigetti|ibm) require API keys
